```
[/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/src/main/index.ts:219-230] 🟡P2
fs:watch 的 close() 与 fsWatcher 置 null 之间存在竞态窗口
代码片段：
  if (fsWatcher) {
    await fsWatcher.close()
    fsWatcher = null   // ← 此行前，若新 watch 调用到来，fsWatcher 不为 null
  }
修复建议：
  // 建议用 try/finally 确保原子性，或引入互斥锁
  try {
    if (fsWatcher) {
      await fsWatcher.close()
    }
  } finally {
    fsWatcher = null
  }
```

